query: SELECT s.id, s.companyName, s.contactEmail, COUNT(c.id) as country_count FROM suppliers s LEFT JOIN supplierCoverageCountries c ON s.id = c.supplierId WHERE s.contactEmail LIKE '%test%' OR s.companyName LIKE '%Test%' GROUP BY s.id LIMIT 10;
